-navigate to src folder

cd catkin_ws/src

- use create_catkin_pkg <package name> <dependent package>

create_catkin_pkg beginner_tutorial std_msgs rospy roscpp

- go to root

cd ~/catkin_ws

- build the workspace. This will update the bash file

catkin_make

- source updated bash 

. ~/catkin_ws/devel/setup.bash

rospack profile
